## CLI Pattern
All skills follow: `uv run python .claude/skills/<name>/<name>.py <subcommand> [args]`
Use `--help` on any script for available subcommands.

## Web Search
- Do NOT use the built-in `web_search` — it requires API keys that are not configured.
- Use this command instead (SearXNG, self-hosted, no API key needed):
  ```bash
  curl -s 'http://localhost:8888/search?q=QUERY&format=json' | python3 -c "
  import sys, json
  r = json.load(sys.stdin)
  for x in r.get('results', [])[:5]:
      print(x['title'])
      print(x['url'])
      print(x.get('content','')[:200])
      print()
  "
  ```
- Replace `QUERY` with URL-encoded search terms (spaces as `+`).

